						<summary>

						<p>This inscription states that the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in the temple of Paramēśvara at Pūvālaikkuḍi was built by one <hi rend="bold">Vāduḷi Ūraṉ Tuṟṟiṉṉai.</hi> This is assignable probably to <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Chōḷa.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
